<p>&nbsp;</p>

     <p>Tompkins Square --
     <BR>an old man teaches Tai-Chi
     <br>to a crowd of pigeons


     <p>on the fire escape
     <br>the breeze shifts direction
     <br>from pizza to chow mein


     <p>manhole cover
     <br>offering incense
     <br>to the skyscraper sky

